    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles with a rough idle and persistent oil leaks, while the transmission exhibits harsh shifting between gears. Additionally, there are visible signs of heavy wear throughout the interior and some rust on the exterior body panels. This is an ideal project car or parts donor for someone with the necessary expertise to address its multiple issues.",
