    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and babied since day one. It looks, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, it's a total gem! If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
