    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, preserved in showroom condition. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and delivers a linear power band through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically, this chassis is beyond reproach: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the variable M differential lock provides exceptional lateral traction. The engine timing is precise following a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service. Suspension kinematics remain tight with factory-spec bushings and dampers. Finished in pristine original paint with zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather, this collector-grade specimen offers a pure, analog driving experience with a fully documented service pedigree.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
